__NAME__ purpose
increment a counter on every catalog access
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<group choice='req'>
	<arg choice='plain'>No</arg>
	<arg choice='plain'>Yes</arg>
</group>
__END__


__NAME__ description
Specify whether the catalog counter file should be increased on every 
access to the catalog.
</para><para>
The counter filename will be <filename>hits.<replaceable>catalog_name</replaceable></filename>, placed in the <filename class='directory'>&ICROOT;/etc/</filename> directory.
__END__

__NAME__ see also
TrackFile
__END__

__NAME__ example
<example>
  <title></title>
  <programlisting>
HitCount Yes
  </programlisting>
</example>
__END__

